  "reference_number": "RUS0862",
  "remarks": "\nNikolay Dmitrievich PESKOV is closely associated with Dmitry Sergeyevich PESKOV by virtue of being his son. \nDmitry Sergeyevich PESKOV, who has been designated since 15/3/2022, is President Putin’s Press Secretary and vocal supporter of the Government of Russia in Russian and international media, and has promoted policies or actions which destabilize Ukraine or undermine or threaten the territorial integrity, sovereignty or independence of Ukraine.  \n The trust services sanctions were imposed on 21/03/2023.",
